{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act39side", "eventName": "出蒼白海", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "EP-6", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "若退路在燃燒", "storyInfo": "安納斯塔西奧帶人圍剿了船員們的營地。看到背後衝天的火光，原本已經被胡安娜放走的棘刺不願就這樣離開，在月色下毅然轉身，奔向營地。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "57_g2_saltdesert_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wind", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$wasteland_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#11$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#8$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）難以置信，那個女人竟然願意放我們離開……本來以為修復失敗後，我們都會被五花大綁交給審判庭。", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#8$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）噓……", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#11$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#4$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，無論說多少次抱歉，都挽回不了你的損失。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#4$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想這就是結局了，伊西多。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心吧，我不會怪你，這不是你的錯。做出選擇的時候，我就已經接受了結果。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，是你為我們承受了船員們的憤怒，也是你保護了帕斯卡拉。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#4$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……或許你也可以和我們一起走。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可以預見，女士，留在這裡你會非常危險。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#11$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快走吧。你們之前不是吵著要跑嗎？現在有機會了，怎麼還不動身？", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#4$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是船隊的首領，我不會拋下我的船員。這是我向科魯茲立下的誓言，這輩子我都不會違背它。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "胡安娜女士，有樣東西……我得還給你。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#4$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那套衣服和劍你就留著吧，就當作是給你的酬勞。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是那些……", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是？", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#5$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "青年將手伸進衣袋，卻突然停住了。他緩緩地吐了口氣。"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後取出了口袋裡的東西。"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "ShowItem", "attributes": {"image": "item_act39side_1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "HideItem", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅盤？不……", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#5$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……我不明白，如果它還安然無恙，那煉金工坊裡的那些殘骸是……？", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#5$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你之前不是在修復羅盤，那這段時間你到底在做什麼？！", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#6$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#6$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說話啊！", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#4$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "實驗裡毀掉的那個羅盤……是我嘗試著複製出來的。真品……我沒動。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#9$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 25.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？！我怎麼不知道……什麼時候的事情？", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#15$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有跟任何人說過……", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不明白，你這麼做的理由是什麼？！", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#6$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅盤上搭載的心相原質……結構遠比我想像的複雜。如果我不能完美地將它複製出來，就說明我很有可能還沒完全理解它的本質。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種情況下貿然去操作真正的心相原質，能預見的幾乎只有失敗。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我不能失敗。你的期望、整支船隊的期盼、極境和帕斯卡拉的命運……都在我身上。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後來，我總忍不住去想，如果注定失敗，至少我該有辦法把損失降到最低。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我一直在試圖複製心相原質。假如事實證明我沒有能力理解心相原質，你們至少還可以帶著真品，去找下一位煉金術師。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還省出了一部分材料，不至於讓船隊彈盡糧絕。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我……", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#4$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起，我確實想盡了辦法。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#4$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多……你覺得這樣就算是盡了全力嗎？", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#6$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我算過，失敗的機率超過百分之八十七……這是我能想到的最保險的辦法。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#4$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "失敗並不足以讓人畏懼，縱然成功的機率只有萬分之一，我也會孤注一擲，傾盡所有去賭一個機會。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是賭博，不是實驗。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈……比起成功的機率，我們擁有第二次機會的可能性才更為渺茫。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#11$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴我，我們的人生到底是賭博，還是實驗？", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#11$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "溫蒂等一下會來接我離開，你打算和我們一起走嗎？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我的旅途還沒有結束。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會繼續下去。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你呢，帕斯卡拉？和我一起走嗎？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#11$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧，至少我能想辦法帶你離開這裡……", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#11$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好……伊西多，你保重。", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#10$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "保重。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，你們也是。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "57_g14_ibtown_n", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#2$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "西爾弗閣下。", "name": "習武教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你願意留下，這很好，很好……", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#2$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您忘了？我的腿一直都不好，去不了。", "name": "習武教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我沒有忘記，你是之前在第二次圍剿時受傷的吧？", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……您就是忘了。我這個腿傷是行刑那天造成的，當初是您為我處理的傷口，結果傷口最後還是感染了。", "name": "習武教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "假如，我是說假如……我當初的醫術沒有這麼差，可以治好你的腿，那你現在會和我們一起去嗎？", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#3$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然了。", "name": "習武教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我知道了。", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0, "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#4$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id"