"focus": "m"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會留您一個人在這裡。", "name": "蒂奇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1580_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是命令，蒂奇。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#7$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footstep_stonestep", "volume": 0.6, "channel": "step1", "loop": "false"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "step1", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "57_g2_saltdesert_n", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_fssand", "channel": "ystep", "loop": "true", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "ystep", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "月色下，伊西多一個人踩在鹽漠上，背後一串孤獨的腳印跟隨著他。"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他不知道自己走了多久，大概有整整一夜。"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g21_skystarry_r2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他覺得自己好像讓很多人失望了，但又不清楚自己到底做錯了什麼。"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "忽然間，他想有個朋友在身邊，又猛地意識到他與極境才剛剛道別。"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多猜想，溫蒂應該已經找到了極境，確認自己的安全後，他們的任務也就結束了。"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許此刻他們正商量著離開鹽漠，繼續下一個任務。而他也會繼續自己的旅程，一個人。"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒什麼不好，沒有任何牽掛。"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "57_g10_community_n", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1592_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "shake", "random": "true", "power": 5.0, "times": 40.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊……哈……", "name": "睏倦的船員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1592_1#1$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早知道晚上不多喝那兩盆鹹鱗汁了……", "name": "睏倦的船員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1592_1#1$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothtrailground", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id"